<section class="magroad" id="newcomer-roadmap" aria-label="Canada Newcomer Roadmap">
 <div class="magroad-inner">
  <h2>The Canada Newcomer Roadmap</h2>
  <p class="magroad-intro">Every successful settlement follows the same financial path. This roadmap shows the exact order to tackle each milestone &mdash; so you always know what comes next on your journey from arrival to long-term financial success in Canada.</p>
  <div class="magroad-steps">
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">1</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Arrival</h3><p>Land in Canada and gather your key documents.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">2</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>SIN Number</h3><p>Apply for your Social Insurance Number &mdash; it is free.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">3</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Bank Account</h3><p>Open a fee-free newcomer chequing account.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">4</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Credit Score</h3><p>Get your first credit card and start building history.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">5</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Housing</h3><p>Rent an apartment, even without Canadian credit.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">6</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Healthcare</h3><p>Register for your provincial health coverage.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">7</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Employment</h3><p>Find work and get credentials recognised.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">8</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Taxes</h3><p>Understand and file your Canadian tax return.</p></div></div>
   <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
   <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">9</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Long-Term Financial Success</h3><p>Grow savings with a TFSA, RRSP, and investing.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="magcta1"><h3>Skip the Guesswork on Building Credit</h3><p>Your credit score is the single biggest hurdle newcomers face. Our step-by-step guide shows you the fastest path to a strong profile from scratch.</p><a href="https://moneyabroadguide.com/building-credit-canada-newcomers-2026/">Get the Credit-Building eBook &rarr;</a></div>
 </div>
</section>
